notes=D8

"Snoopy’s Collar (D8) faces southeast and connects the South Face to the col between The Citadel’s summits and it is steeper than the South Face below it. The South Face opens up for wider turns into a gully between the rocks."

https://www.frontrangeskimo.com/citadel/
