notes=D3

https://www.frontrangeskimo.com/goldenbear/

"The east and south slopes of the peak are located within the ski area. The northeast bowls connecting Golden Bear to Hagar are outside of the ski area. The Northeast Bowl, described here, is accessed from Dry Gulch. A great day can be had combining a route on Hagar or Citadel with Golden Bear"
id=8adb61ca-af5a-440b-a2c7-abdd840f77d3
